{
  "stem": "20684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took the doctors with them for their own use and executed them somewhere further down the line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't know so I kept on looking for him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I kept on looking for him right up until about 1946, '47.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For about two or three years I kept on writing letters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wrote letters to Stalin, I wrote letters to Churchill.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't answer me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't think I was important, I suppose, and so-- they played a game with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People played a game with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People through I was stupid, which I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But still, they said, why don't you write to Churchill, why don't you write to Stalin to tell me where my father was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, different people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In an orphanage-- when I was in the displaced people's camp and orphanage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that came to an end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We reunited with my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We come back to our village-- a town, not village, a town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was summer, the weather was warm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I can't remember the day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'd be lying to you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I can look up the date and I know where it was, but I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was towards the end of '44 and it was before-- well, not end but about August, September '44.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would have gone in before that because we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In '45 was already that-- now I'm getting confused.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it is '45.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, because it wasn't my ninth birthday that I was given the bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Must have been-- I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't want to-- to speculate.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
